    <releaseNotes>
    - New: Book polishing: Add option to embed all referenced fonts when polishing books using the 'Polish Books' tool.
    - New: DOCX Input: Add support for clickable (hyperlinked) images
    - New: DOCX Input: Insert page breaks at the start of every new section
	- New: Drivers for Trekstor Pyrus Maxi and PocketBook Surfpad 2
	- New: DOCX Input: Add support for horizontal rules created by typing three hyphens and pressing enter.
    - Fixed: Fix detection of SD Card in some PRS-T2N devices
    - Fixed: MOBI Input: Fix a regression that broke parsing of MOBI files with malformed markup that also used entities for apostrophes.
    - Fixed: Get Books: Update Woblink store plugin
    - Fixed: Metadata download dialog: Prevent the buttons from being re-ordered when the Next button is clicked.
    - Fixed: PDF Output: Fix links that point to URLs with query parameters being mangled by the conversion process.
	- Fixed: DOCX Input: Fix links pointing to locations in the same document that contain multiple, redundant bookmarks not working.
	- Fixed: EPUB/AZW3 Output: Fix splitting on page-break-after with plain text immediately following the split point causing the text to be added before rather than after the split point.
	- Fixed: DOCX Input: handle bookmarks defined at the paragraph level
	- Fixed: DOCX Input: Handle hyperlinks created as fields
	- New News Source: Democracy Now by Antoine Beaupre
    - Improved News Source: iprofessional
    </releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
</package>
